@startuml
title ElectroCorp Web App - Notifications Frontend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Notifications Frontend Bounded Context" {
  class "Domain" as Frontend_notifications_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Application" as Frontend_notifications_Application <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Frontend_notifications_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Presentation" as Frontend_notifications_Presentation <<layer>>
}

Frontend_notifications_Presentation ..> Frontend_notifications_Application : user actions / state
Frontend_notifications_Application ..> Frontend_notifications_Domain : models and rules
Frontend_notifications_Application ..> Frontend_notifications_Infrastructure : API services / adapters
Frontend_notifications_Infrastructure ..> Frontend_notifications_Domain : resources and mappers
Frontend_notifications_Presentation ..> Frontend_notifications_Domain : view models

note bottom of Frontend_notifications_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/frontend/layers/notifications.
end note

@enduml
